<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="es">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>RADIANCE LAB – Lista de Precios</title>
<link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Cormorant+Garamond:wght@300;400;600;700&family=Rajdhani:wght@300;400;500;600;700&family=Montserrat:wght@200;300;400;600&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
<style>
  :root {
    --black: #050608;
    --night-blue: #0a0e1a;
    --blue-metal: #1a2744;
    --blue-glow: #1e3a6e;
    --silver: #a8b4c4;
    --silver-light: #c8d4e4;
    --silver-bright: #e0e8f0;
    --gold-accent: #8a9ab0;
    --text-main: #d0dcea;
    --text-muted: #6a7d96;
    --price-color: #7eb8e8;
    --border: rgba(168,180,196,0.18);
    --glow: rgba(30,58,110,0.6);
  }

  * { margin: 0; padding: 0; box-sizing: border-box; }

  html { scroll-behavior: smooth; }

  body {
    background-color: var(--black);
    color: var(--text-main);
    font-family: 'Montserrat', sans-serif;
    overflow-x: hidden;
  }

  /* ── PARTICLES ── */
  #particles {
    position: fixed;
    top: 0; left: 0;
    width: 100%; height: 100%;
    pointer-events: none;
    z-index: 0;
  }

  /* ── HERO ── */
  .hero {
    position: relative;
    min-height: 100vh;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    overflow: hidden;
    z-index: 1;
  }

  .hero-bg {
    position: absolute;
    inset: 0;
    background:
      radial-gradient(ellipse 80% 60% at 50% 40%, rgba(26,39,68,0.85) 0%, transparent 70%),
      linear-gradient(180deg, #050608 0%, #0a0e1a 50%, #050608 100%);
    z-index: 0;
  }

  .hero-logo-ring {
    position: relative;
    z-index: 2;
    width: 160px;
    height: 160px;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
  }

  .hero-logo-ring svg {
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    animation: spinRing 18s linear infinite;
  }

  @keyframes spinRing {
    from { transform: rotate(0deg); }
    to   { transform: rotate(360deg); }
  }

  .logo-inner {
    position: absolute;
    inset: 0;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    font-family: 'Rajdhani', sans-serif;
    font-size: 1rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    letter-spacing: 0.3em;
    color: var(--silver-bright);
    text-transform: uppercase;
  }

  .hero-title {
    position: relative;
    z-index: 2;
    font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;
    font-size: clamp(3.5rem, 10vw, 8rem);
    font-weight: 300;
    letter-spacing: 0.25em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #e0e8f0 0%, #a8b4c4 40%, #ffffff 60%, #7090b0 100%);
    -webkit-background-clip: text;
    -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
    background-clip: text;
    text-align: center;
    line-height: 1;
    animation: fadeUp 1.2s ease forwards;
  }

  .hero-sub {
    position: relative;
    z-index: 2;
    font-family: 'Rajdhani', sans-serif;
    font-size: clamp(0.7rem, 2vw, 1rem);
    font-weight: 400;
    letter-spacing: 0.5em;
    color: var(--silver);
    text-transform: uppercase;
    margin-top: 0.5rem;
    animation: fadeUp 1.5s ease forwards;
    opacity: 0;
    animation-delay: 0.3s;
    animation-fill-mode: forwards;
  }

  .hero-tagline {
    position: relative;
    z-index: 2;
    font-family: 'Montserrat', sans-serif;
    font-size: clamp(0.6rem, 1.5vw, 0.78rem);
    font-weight: 300;
    letter-spacing: 0.35em;
    color: var(--silver-light);
    text-transform: uppercase;
    margin-top: 1.5rem;
    text-align: center;
    max-width: 600px;
    padding: 0 1rem;
    opacity: 0;
    animation: fadeUp 1.8s ease forwards;
    animation-delay: 0.6s;
    animation-fill-mode: forwards;
  }

  .hero-line {
    position: relative;
    z-index: 2;
    width: 120px;
    height: 1px;
    background: linear-gradient(90deg, transparent, var(--silver), transparent);
    margin: 1.5rem auto 0;
    animation: expandLine 2s ease forwards;
    animation-delay: 0.9s;
    opacity: 0;
  }

  .hero-badges {
    position: relative;
    z-index: 2;
    display: flex;
    gap: 1.5rem;
    margin-top: 2.5rem;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    justify-content: center;
    opacity: 0;
    animation: fadeUp 2s ease forwards;
    animation-delay: 1.1s;
    animation-fill-mode: forwards;
  }

  .badge {
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    padding: 0.45rem 1.2rem;
    font-family: 'Rajdhani', sans-serif;
    font-size: 0.65rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.3em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--silver);
    background: rgba(26,39,68,0.3);
    backdrop-filter: blur(4px);
    transition: all 0.4s;
    cursor: default;
  }

  .badge:hover {
    border-color: var(--silver-light);
    color: var(--silver-bright);
    background: rgba(26,39,68,0.6);
    box-shadow: 0 0 20px rgba(126,184,232,0.15);
  }

  .scroll-indicator {
    position: absolute;
    bottom: 2rem;
    left: 50%;
    transform: translateX(-50%);
    z-index: 2;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 0.5rem;
    opacity: 0.5;
    animation: bounce 2s infinite;
  }

  .scroll-indicator span {
    font-size: 0.55rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.4em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--silver);
  }

  .scroll-arrow {
    width: 1px;
    height: 40px;
    background: linear-gradient(180deg, var(--silver), transparent);
  }

  @keyframes bounce {
    0%, 100% { transform: translateX(-50%) translateY(0); }
    50% { transform: translateX(-50%) translateY(8px); }
  }

  /* ── KEYFRAMES ── */
  @keyframes fadeUp {
    from { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(30px); }
    to   { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }
  }

  @keyframes expandLine {
    from { opacity: 0; width: 0; }
    to   { opacity: 1; width: 120px; }
  }

  /* ── SECTION BASE ── */
  .section {
    position: relative;
    z-index: 1;
    padding: 6rem 2rem;
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  .section-inner {
    max-width: 960px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  /* ── PARALLAX SLIDES ── */
  .parallax-bg {
    position: absolute;
    inset: 0;
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  .slide-track {
    display: flex;
    width: 400%;
    height: 100%;
    animation: slideImages 28s linear infinite;
  }

  .slide-track img {
    width: 25%;
    height: 100%;
    object-fit: cover;
    opacity: 0.12;
    filter: grayscale(30%) brightness(0.6) saturate(1.2);
  }

  @keyframes slideImages {
    0%   { transform: translateX(0); }
    100% { transform: translateX(-50%); }
  }

  .parallax-overlay {
    position: absolute;
    inset: 0;
    background: linear-gradient(180deg,
      var(--black) 0%,
      rgba(5,6,8,0.75) 30%,
      rgba(5,6,8,0.75) 70%,
      var(--black) 100%);
  }

  /* ── TECH INTRO ── */
  .tech-section {
    background: linear-gradient(180deg, var(--black) 0%, var(--night-blue) 50%, var(--black) 100%);
  }

  .section-eyebrow {
    font-family: 'Rajdhani', sans-serif;
    font-size: 0.65rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.5em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--price-color);
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    opacity: 0.8;
  }

  .section-title {
    font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;
    font-size: clamp(2rem, 5vw, 3.5rem);
    font-weight: 300;
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
    color: var(--silver-bright);
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    line-height: 1.1;
  }

  .section-body {
    font-size: 0.82rem;
    line-height: 1.9;
    color: var(--text-muted);
    max-width: 700px;
    font-weight: 300;
  }

  .tech-cards {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(260px, 1fr));
    gap: 1.5rem;
    margin-top: 3rem;
  }

  .tech-card {
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    padding: 2rem 1.5rem;
    background: rgba(26,39,68,0.2);
    backdrop-filter: blur(8px);
    transition: all 0.5s;
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  .tech-card::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    top: 0; left: 0;
    width: 100%; height: 2px;
    background: linear-gradient(90deg, transparent, var(--price-color), transparent);
    transform: scaleX(0);
    transition: transform 0.5s;
  }

  .tech-card:hover::before { transform: scaleX(1); }
  .tech-card:hover {
    border-color: rgba(126,184,232,0.3);
    background: rgba(26,39,68,0.4);
    transform: translateY(-4px);
    box-shadow: 0 20px 60px rgba(0,0,0,0.4);
  }

  .tech-card-icon {
    font-size: 2rem;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    display: block;
  }

  .tech-card-title {
    font-family: 'Rajdhani', sans-serif;
    font-size: 1rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    letter-spacing: 0.2em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--silver-bright);
    margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
  }

  .tech-card-body {
    font-size: 0.76rem;
    line-height: 1.8;
    color: var(--text-muted);
    font-weight: 300;
  }

  /* ── DIVIDER ── */
  .divider {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 1.5rem;
    margin: 4rem auto;
    max-width: 400px;
  }
  .divider-line {
    flex: 1;
    height: 1px;
    background: linear-gradient(90deg, transparent, var(--border));
  }
  .divider-line:last-child {
    background: linear-gradient(90deg, var(--border), transparent);
  }
  .divider-diamond {
    width: 6px;
    height: 6px;
    background: var(--silver);
    transform: rotate(45deg);
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }

  /* ── PRICE AREA ── */
  .price-area {
    margin-bottom: 5rem;
  }

  .area-header {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 1.5rem;
    margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
  }

  .area-number {
    font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;
    font-size: 4rem;
    font-weight: 300;
    color: rgba(168,180,196,0.12);
    line-height: 1;
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }

  .area-title-wrap {}

  .area-tag {
    font-family: 'Rajdhani', sans-serif;
    font-size: 0.6rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.5em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--price-color);
    margin-bottom: 0.3rem;
  }

  .area-title {
    font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;
    font-size: clamp(1.6rem, 4vw, 2.4rem);
    font-weight: 400;
    letter-spacing: 0.08em;
    color: var(--silver-bright);
  }

  .area-desc {
    font-size: 0.78rem;
    line-height: 1.85;
    color: var(--text-muted);
    margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
    max-width: 720px;
    font-weight: 300;
  }

  .price-table {
    border-collapse: collapse;
    width: 100%;
  }

  .price-table tr {
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
    transition: all 0.3s;
  }

  .price-table tr:hover {
    background: rgba(26,39,68,0.35);
  }

  .price-table td {
    padding: 1.1rem 1rem;
    font-size: 0.8rem;
  }

  .price-table td:first-child {
    color: var(--text-main);
    font-weight: 300;
    letter-spacing: 0.03em;
  }

  .price-table td:last-child {
    text-align: right;
    font-family: 'Rajdhani', sans-serif;
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--price-color);
    letter-spacing: 0.05em;
    white-space: nowrap;
  }

  .price-dot {
    display: inline-block;
    width: 4px;
    height: 4px;
    background: var(--price-color);
    border-radius: 50%;
    margin-right: 0.8rem;
    vertical-align: middle;
    opacity: 0.6;
  }

  /* ── HIGHLIGHT BOX ── */
  .highlight-box {
    border: 1px solid rgba(126,184,232,0.25);
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(26,39,68,0.4), rgba(10,14,26,0.6));
    padding: 2rem 2.5rem;
    margin: 2.5rem 0;
    position: relative;
  }

  .highlight-box::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    top: 0; left: 0;
    width: 3px;
    height: 100%;
    background: linear-gradient(180deg, var(--price-color), transparent);
  }

  .highlight-box-title {
    font-family: 'Rajdhani', sans-serif;
    font-size: 0.7rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.4em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--price-color);
    margin-bottom: 0.8rem;
  }

  .highlight-box p {
    font-size: 0.78rem;
    line-height: 1.85;
    color: var(--text-muted);
    font-weight: 300;
  }

  /* ── CONTACT ── */
  .contact-section {
    position: relative;
    padding: 8rem 2rem;
    text-align: center;
    overflow: hidden;
    background: linear-gradient(180deg, var(--black) 0%, var(--night-blue) 60%, var(--black) 100%);
  }

  .contact-glow {
    position: absolute;
    top: 50%;
    left: 50%;
    transform: translate(-50%, -50%);
    width: 600px;
    height: 600px;
    background: radial-gradient(circle, rgba(30,58,110,0.4) 0%, transparent 70%);
    pointer-events: none;
  }

  .contact-title {
    position: relative;
    z-index: 1;
    font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;
    font-size: clamp(1.5rem, 4vw, 2.5rem);
    font-weight: 300;
    letter-spacing: 0.15em;
    color: var(--silver-bright);
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }

  .contact-sub {
    font-family: 'Rajdhani', sans-serif;
    font-size: 0.7rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.4em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--text-muted);
    position: relative;
    z-index: 1;
    margin-bottom: 3rem;
  }

  .phone-display {
    position: relative;
    z-index: 1;
    display: inline-block;
    font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;
    font-size: clamp(2.5rem, 8vw, 5rem);
    font-weight: 300;
    letter-spacing: 0.15em;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #e0e8f0 0%, #a8b4c4 40%, #7eb8e8 70%, #ffffff 100%);
    -webkit-background-clip: text;
    -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
    background-clip: text;
    text-decoration: none;
    transition: all 0.4s;
    cursor: pointer;
  }

  .phone-display:hover {
    letter-spacing: 0.2em;
    filter: brightness(1.2);
  }

  .phone-label {
    display: block;
    position: relative;
    z-index: 1;
    font-size: 0.65rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.5em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--text-muted);
    margin-top: 1rem;
  }

  .whatsapp-btn {
    position: relative;
    z-index: 1;
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 0.75rem;
    margin-top: 2.5rem;
    padding: 0.9rem 2.5rem;
    border: 1px solid rgba(37,211,102,0.4);
    color: #5dcc85;
    font-family: 'Rajdhani', sans-serif;
    font-size: 0.8rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    letter-spacing: 0.3em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    text-decoration: none;
    background: rgba(37,211,102,0.07);
    transition: all 0.4s;
  }

  .whatsapp-btn:hover {
    background: rgba(37,211,102,0.15);
    border-color: rgba(37,211,102,0.6);
    box-shadow: 0 0 30px rgba(37,211,102,0.15);
    transform: translateY(-2px);
  }

  /* ── FOOTER ── */
  footer {
    border-top: 1px solid var(--border);
    padding: 2rem;
    text-align: center;
    font-size: 0.65rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.3em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--text-muted);
    background: var(--black);
  }

  /* ── REVEAL ON SCROLL ── */
  .reveal {
    opacity: 0;
    transform: translateY(40px);
    transition: opacity 0.9s ease, transform 0.9s ease;
  }
  .reveal.visible {
    opacity: 1;
    transform: translateY(0);
  }
  .reveal-left {
    opacity: 0;
    transform: translateX(-40px);
    transition: opacity 0.9s ease, transform 0.9s ease;
  }
  .reveal-left.visible {
    opacity: 1;
    transform: translateX(0);
  }

  /* ── FLOATING NAV ── */
  .float-nav {
    position: fixed;
    top: 50%;
    right: 1.5rem;
    transform: translateY(-50%);
    z-index: 100;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 0.6rem;
  }

  .nav-dot {
    width: 6px;
    height: 6px;
    border: 1px solid var(--silver);
    border-radius: 50%;
    cursor: pointer;
    transition: all 0.3s;
    opacity: 0.4;
  }

  .nav-dot:hover, .nav-dot.active {
    opacity: 1;
    background: var(--silver);
    transform: scale(1.4);
  }

  /* ── AREA SEPARATOR ── */
  .area-sep {
    height: 1px;
    background: linear-gradient(90deg, transparent, var(--border), transparent);
    margin: 5rem 0;
  }

  @media (max-width: 600px) {
    .hero-badges { gap: 0.8rem; }
    .badge { font-size: 0.55rem; padding: 0.4rem 0.9rem; }
    .float-nav { display: none; }
    .tech-cards { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
  }
</style>
</head>
<body>

<!-- Particle canvas -->
<canvas id="particles"></canvas>

<!-- Floating nav dots -->
<nav class="float-nav" id="floatNav">
  <div class="nav-dot active" data-target="hero" title="Inicio"></div>
  <div class="nav-dot" data-target="tech" title="Tecnología"></div>
  <div class="nav-dot" data-target="fresado" title="Fresado"></div>
  <div class="nav-dot" data-target="impresion" title="Impresión 3D"></div>
  <div class="nav-dot" data-target="termoformado" title="Termoformado"></div>
  <div class="nav-dot" data-target="otras" title="Otras Áreas"></div>
  <div class="nav-dot" data-target="contacto" title="Contacto"></div>
</nav>

<!-- ── HERO ── -->
<section class="hero" id="hero">
  <div class="hero-bg"></div>

  <div class="hero-logo-ring">
    <svg viewBox="0 0 160 160" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
      <circle cx="80" cy="80" r="74" stroke="url(#ringGrad)" stroke-width="1" stroke-dasharray="4 6"/>
      <circle cx="80" cy="80" r="64" stroke="rgba(168,180,196,0.2)" stroke-width="0.5"/>
      <defs>
        <linearGradient id="ringGrad" x1="0" y1="0" x2="160" y2="160" gradientUnits="userSpaceOnUse">
          <stop offset="0%" stop-color="#e0e8f0"/>
          <stop offset="50%" stop-color="#4070a0"/>
          <stop offset="100%" stop-color="#e0e8f0"/>
        </linearGradient>
      </defs>
    </svg>
    <div class="logo-inner">RL</div>
  </div>

  <h1 class="hero-title">RADIANCE LAB</h1>
  <p class="hero-sub">Laboratorio Dental Especializado</p>
  <p class="hero-tagline">Calidad e implementación de tecnología en 3D a precios justos</p>
  <div class="hero-line"></div>

  <div class="hero-badges">
    <div class="badge">CAD / CAM</div>
    <div class="badge">Diseño &amp; Impresión 3D</div>
    <div class="badge">Escaneo Intraoral Digital</div>
  </div>

  <div class="scroll-indicator">
    <span>Explorar</span>
    <div class="scroll-arrow"></div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- ── TECH INTRO ── -->
<section class="section tech-section" id="tech">
  <!-- Background slides with printer images -->
  <div class="parallax-bg">
    <div class="slide-track" id="slideTech">
      <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1612815154858-60aa4c59eaa6?w=1600&q=80" alt="3D Printer" loading="lazy">
      <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1581091226825-a6a2a5aee158?w=1600&q=80" alt="Technology" loading="lazy">
      <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1628863353691-0071c8c1874c?w=1600&q=80" alt="3D Print Detail" loading="lazy">
      <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1581092580497-e0d23cbdf1dc?w=1600&q=80" alt="Lab Technology" loading="lazy">
      <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1612815154858-60aa4c59eaa6?w=1600&q=80" alt="3D Printer" loading="lazy">
      <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1581091226825-a6a2a5aee158?w=1600&q=80" alt="Technology" loading="lazy">
      <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1628863353691-0071c8c1874c?w=1600&q=80" alt="3D Print Detail" loading="lazy">
      <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1581092580497-e0d23cbdf1dc?w=1600&q=80" alt="Lab Technology" loading="lazy">
    </div>
    <div class="parallax-overlay"></div>
  </div>

  <div class="section-inner" style="position:relative;z-index:2;">
    <p class="section-eyebrow reveal">Nuestra Tecnología</p>
    <h2 class="section-title reveal">Innovación en Cada<br>Restauración</h2>
    <p class="section-body reveal">
      En RADIANCE LAB trabajamos con las tecnologías más avanzadas disponibles en el sector odontológico. 
      Contamos con impresoras 3D de alta resolución como la <strong style="color:var(--silver-light)">Photon Mono 4</strong>, 
      la <strong style="color:var(--silver-light)">Halot Mage S</strong> y la 
      <strong style="color:var(--silver-light)">Elegoo Saturn 4 Ultra 16K</strong>, capaces de producir 
      restauraciones con precisión de micras. Nuestros escáneres intraorales digitales eliminan la necesidad 
      de impresiones físicas, garantizando comodidad al paciente y exactitud en cada caso.
    </p>

    <div class="tech-cards">
